0/extras/dcd78346b93a98d5b7f67527f6acd492.poster.avif?t=1743236342\" width=600 height=90 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1852860/extras/dcd78346b93a98d5b7f67527f6acd492.webm?t=1743236342\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1852860/extras/dcd78346b93a98d5b7f67527f6acd492.mp4?t=1743236342\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Yet one thing has always eluded this wanderer…<br><br>They say that he who can best The Black Labyrinth - a place of trials and battles unimaginable - and raise The Axe within… shall become…<br><br><strong>CHAMPION OF THE ANCIENTS</strong></i>",
